      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should be a resident of Bihar.\n1. The applicant should be a farmer.\n1. The applicant must be registered on the DBT portal.\n1. Farmers who have taken advantage of the scheme in the last three years (202-22, 2022-23 and 2023-24) will not be given the benefit of the scheme this year.\n\n<br>\n\n> **Note:**  \n\n\n1. The benefit of this scheme will be given only once to one member of the family.\n1. Beneficiaries will be selected on first come first serve basis.\n\n<br>\n\n<br>\n\n",
